wblut.geom2D
Class WB_Voronoi2D

java.lang.Object
  wblut.geom2D.WB_Voronoi2D

public class WB_Voronoi2D
extends java.lang.Object

Stripped version of Zhenyu Pan's JAVA transcription of Shane O'Sullivan's C implementation of Fortune's sweep algorithm. I added degenerate point detection. http://shaneosullivan.wordpress.com/2007/04/05/fortunes-sweep-line-voronoi- algorithm-implemented-in-java/

Author:
Frederik Vanhoutte, W:Blut, extremely derivative
